            =image_tag "https://s3.amazonaws.com/lorious/layout/elements/landing_page/1.svg", class: "list-number"
            %h3 Find the right expert at the right price.
            %p Browse our list of experts, or tell us about your challenge, and weâ€™ll find you the right person.
